data.description: Welcome to this cozy 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath home located in the heart of Bay City. You'll find a convenient main floor bedroom with two additional upstairs. This property boasts a spacious, open kitchen that is perfect for family gatherings. The well-lit full basement provides ample space for storage or for future expansion of additional rooms. With some new flooring, you can unlock this home's full potential and make it your own. The backyard features a lovely patio, offering outdoor space for barbecues and entertaining. Call today for a showing! OPEN HOUSE Thursday 11/9 (5-7PM)
